{"tid":1219972,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[好撚急!!!!!!] 韓國MBC要人今日接受訪問 唔洗識韓文!!","createTime":"2019-06-14T02:05:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:46:00.000Z","uid":261014,"like":215,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6b359075e988342424fbfe5461e35d10f873fb","tid":1219972,"uid":261014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:05:33.000Z","msg":"我已經幫手聯絡咗韓國MBC<br />\n佢地需要以下嘅人今日香港時間6點前接受訪問<br />\n<br />\n1. 有份做前線 <br />\n2. 有份見到警狗打人同暴力對待我地<br />\n3. 急救站<br />\n4. 學生會代表<br />\n<br />\n內容大概講下當日嘅情況 警狗點樣對我地 專注報導黑警嘅惡行<br />\n<br />\n唔洗識韓文 到時會有翻譯<br />\n翻譯個個識普通話同英文<br />\n會幫你遮樣 會幫你變聲<br />\n<br />\n訪問地點： 香港 (可以盡量就你地)<br />\n<br />\n如果有願意接受訪問嘅義士請留低tg 唔該曬大家!! <br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死黑警"},{"pid":"0ea7607aaaac44911a6428ee442cb71e8ced70d3","tid":1219972,"uid":261014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:06:07.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafbcfa3d8348d632312bb5e145fab976d54d04d","tid":1219972,"uid":2718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3fcf243b95396362337fcff81586fea6e43f9318","tid":1219972,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:10:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d157b82721e8d37a38f5f3e43c7b04aefaa87941","tid":1219972,"uid":185544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:13:42.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"27ab01161c94e2df346ef1095890039de8ff9798","tid":1219972,"uid":260460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0badf623420a596be4524730a325fc209ea9a9aa","tid":1219972,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"da78d3e4a2f7303d9325c29397db7ff3b4bd68da","tid":1219972,"uid":49228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"723ea6195e67895db6b1a499ccb1cba7d7284b3e","tid":1219972,"uid":185544,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"7出國際"},{"pid":"bc03db22679ffb544737c29b98bb95e61239f2b5","tid":1219972,"uid":258746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:15:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6e30501bcca21a01f207d6a424a3f994943bb04","tid":1219972,"uid":113241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"288ce7ec56c7a3c36db3ae558899fb3d7da182cd","tid":1219972,"uid":5809,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:15:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<br />\n &mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁多位香港人,大家認為星期日上街係為左咩!?<br />\n<br />\n為左抗惡法?無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為咗迫林鄭下台?無錯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但最重要既係保護香港人!!!!!!!!!!</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2094c4de2c3d7776ecf1a01f5ae5aa07fce9e4de","tid":1219972,"uid":3077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:16:03.000Z","msg"